YELLOW JACKET pressed the pace to the top of the lane and weakened in the drive. DYNAMIC DEVOTION lost position in the turn and came again down the lane for the minor award. MOON CHARGER well placed to track the pace for the first three-eighths and failed to mount a rally in the stretch. REAPPLY failed to menace. MISTER EZRA was never a factor. WORK FROM HOME showed some early speed and faded.
